								<div class="rich-text"><p>What do you treasure? An object, a person, a memory? Here in the Westpac Long Gallery you will discover 100 of the Australian Museum’s greatest treasures. Some are treasures because they are very old; some because they are very rare. Others are treasures because of the stories they tell: who made them, who found them or who owned them; a story about the Museum; about Australia and its history; or about the wonders of the natural world.</p><p>Enter the gallery and discover the stories behind 100 treasures of the Australian Museum.</p></div>
